# docs/design — Wanted Design hand-off bundle
# Track design material (HTML + JSX) but exclude bundled React runtime (npm-derivable)
docs/design/wanted-bundle/33122b9e-*.js
docs/design/wanted-bundle/93aa0060-*.js

# docs/design/livemetro — Offline hand-off mirror of ~/Downloads/livemetro.
# Track audit essentials (src/ + lib/ + uploads/ + LiveMetro*.html + README).
# Ignore self-contained standalone exports (~25MB each — content duplicates project/src/)
# and export/ subtree (also duplicates src/ + lib/).
docs/design/livemetro/project/LiveMetro standalone.html
docs/design/livemetro/project/export/

# Transient working files (per-session dumps, never committed)
#   .tmp/         — design-fetch artifacts (HTML/JSX scaffolds from claude.ai/design)
#   dev/active/   — in-flight working notes (handoff/context/tasks markdown)
#   PR_BODY_TMP.md — one-shot PR description draft
#   /pasted-*.png — accidentally-dropped clipboard images at repo root
.tmp/
dev/active/
PR_BODY_TMP.md
/pasted-*.png

# Harness fork backups (created during chore/fork-aos-harness; safe to remove after verification)
/.claude.bak.*/
/.github/workflows.bak.*/

# Superpowers brainstorm visual companion sessions
/.superpowers/

# Playwright MCP test artifacts (snapshots, console logs)
/.playwright-mcp/
